  21 Aug 2003; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org>
  divx4linux-20030428-r1.ebuild, divx4linux-20030428.ebuild:
  These versions do not work with nvrec, adding to divx4linux depends because
  blocking specific versions of divx4linux from the nvrec ebuild does not seem
  to work.

